&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5+ years at a Big 4 firm or in a senior corporate controllership role, with direct involvement in SEC reporting, SOX 404, or complex consolidations.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience drafting or reviewing 10-K/10-Q footnotes, MD&amp;amp;A, or technical accounting memos.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possesses experience with at least one publication in a reputable accounting journal or outlet.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Teaching experience as a professor&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
