&lt;li&gt;8+ years of experience in digital media sales, working with Fortune 500 companies and advertising agencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Established relationships with marketing decision-makers at companies and agencies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven track record of developing and growing a book of business.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exceptional communication and presentation skills, with the ability to articulate complex ideas clearly.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep understanding of X, the social media landscape, and opportunities for marketers to leverage these platforms.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor’s degree (BA/BS) or equivalent relevant experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
