&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Vertical experience in retail, dining, technology, automotive, travel, media &amp;amp; entertainment, or consumer packaged goods.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong aptitude for creative problem-solving and a preference for working in small, collaborative teams.&lt;/li&gt;
