&lt;p&gt;2 Coding Assessments: Solve problems in Rust, C++, or Golang&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Systems Hands-On: Demonstrate practical skills in a live problem-solving session.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Project Deep-Dive: Present your past exceptional work to a small audience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
