&lt;li&gt;Profiling, debugging, and optimizing GPU utilization for multimodal model training and inference.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Building scalable infrastructure for multimodal data management and crawling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hardware / Software / Algorithm co-design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ideal Experiences&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong engineering skills with passion to improve different aspects of data and model.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Has worked on one or more modalities other than text for model training/serving optimization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keeping up with state-of-the-art techniques for preparing multimodal training data.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
