&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;As a Mechanical Engineer&lt;strong&gt; (HVAC/Chilled Water) &lt;/strong&gt;at xAI, you&#39;ll join, diving into the design, analysis, and rollout of advanced mechanical systems for our state-of-the-art facilities. Working onsite with cross-disciplinary teams, you’ll leverage your expertise in HVAC, chilled water distribution, and thermal management to tackle complex challenges, ensuring our infrastructure is efficient, reliable, and scalable. Expect to optimize systems, align solutions with industry standards, and drive sustainability to support xAI’s mission of powering human scientific discovery through AI.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Design &amp;amp; Planning:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
