&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s Degree in Mechanical Engineering or related field. Master&#39;s degree preferred.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
