&lt;li&gt;Proficiency in Python and/or TypeScript.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong understanding of the HTTP protocol and secure API design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Robust engineering background, preferably in fields such as Computer Science, Mathematics, Software Engineering, Physics, or Data Science.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
