&lt;li&gt;Ability to work with massive datasets, optimize system performance, and scale solutions for high-throughput, mission-critical workloads.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with infrastructure-as-code tools like Pulumi or Terraform, particularly in secure or government-aligned deployments.&lt;/li&gt;
