&lt;li&gt;Strong engineering background with expertise in LLMs, agentic systems, and epistemics in AI.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in prompting engineering, synthetic data creation, and long-form text generation using models&lt;/li&gt;
