&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with techniques for ensuring factual accuracy in AI outputs, such as retrieval-augmented generation (RAG) or epistemic uncertainty modeling.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hands-on work with large-scale data processing and generation, focusing on quality, verifiability, and bias mitigation.&lt;/li&gt;
