&lt;li&gt;Vector databases&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Spark&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Focus&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and develop a real-time, web-scale search engine for LLM agent consumption, with a core goal of supporting maximum truth-seeking capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and develop advanced techniques for precise and efficient search indexing, retrieval, and ranking at trillion-document scale across modalities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Integrate the search engine with xAI&#39;s core models to improve accuracy, speed, and relevance in real-time agent interactions, ensuring agents can discern and prioritize truthful information, while minimizing hallucinations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure robustness and scalability of search infrastructure under high-load conditions while aligning with truth-seeking objectives.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
