&lt;li&gt;Expertise in building web-scale search engines, including but not limited to: indexing, information retrieval, search ranking, hybrid search, structured search, and semantic search.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong engineering background with a passion for building high-performance, scalable distributed systems and optimizing latency and throughput.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with LLMs, agents, embedding models, or knowledge-intensive tasks, including fine-tuning for retrieval tasks aimed at enhancing truthfulness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proficient in managing and curating large datasets from diverse sources, with a focus on quality, verifiability, and efficiency to support maximum truth-seeking agents.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preference for candidates with extensive experience in building and scaling web-scale search engines, including hands-on involvement in production systems and experimental iterations.&lt;/li&gt;
