&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About xAI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;xAI’s mission is to create AI systems that can accurately understand the universe and aid humanity in its pursuit of knowledge. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Our team is small, highly motivated, and focused on engineering excellence. This organization is for individuals who appreciate challenging themselves and thrive on curiosity. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We operate with a flat organizational structure. All employees are expected to be hands-on and to contribute directly to the company’s mission. Leadership is given to those who show initiative and consistently deliver excellence. Work ethic and strong prioritization skills are important. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;All engineers are expected to have strong communication skills. They should be able to concisely and accurately share knowledge with their teammates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;We&#39;re seeking an exceptional Android engineer to join a small, high-impact team dedicated to creating the world&#39;s most valuable AI application, judged by the impact it delivers to users. You&#39;ll shape cutting-edge mobile experiences, blending technical mastery with a keen product sense to deliver brilliance that resonates with users. An ideal candidate meets at least the following requirements:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Proficient in Kotlin, Jetpack Compose and reactive programming.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Experienced in architecting modern large production apps while embodying technical excellence.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Strong sense of ownership and agency. Able to put on multiple hats and take responsibility for large areas.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Has a strong product sense and high craft bar. Builds intuitive and delightful user experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Able to optimize for performance, stability and reliability.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Additionally, experience in any of the following may set you apart:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Deep expertise in the Android ecosystem and related development tools (Android Studio, Gradle, etc.).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Experience with media (video, audio, live streaming, etc).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;A proven track record of shipping standout apps or features that demonstrate both technical excellence and exceptional product intuition.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Experience in other functions, such as iOS, full-stack, data science, etc.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Rust for working with our backend components.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Base salary is just one part of our total rewards package at xAI, which also includes equity, comprehensive medical, vision, and dental coverage, access to a 401(k) retirement plan, short &amp;amp; long-term disability insurance, life insurance, and various other discounts and perks.&lt;/p&gt;
