&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;About xAI&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;xAI’s mission is to create AI systems that can accurately understand the universe and aid humanity in its pursuit of knowledge. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Our team is small, highly motivated, and focused on engineering excellence. This organization is for individuals who appreciate challenging themselves and thrive on curiosity. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We operate with a flat organizational structure. All employees are expected to be hands-on and to contribute directly to the company’s mission. Leadership is given to those who show initiative and consistently deliver excellence. Work ethic and strong prioritization skills are important. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;All engineers are expected to have strong communication skills. They should be able to concisely and accurately share knowledge with their teammates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are seeking an experienced Revenue Manager to own end-to-end revenue processes in a high-growth AI company. This role will ensure accurate revenue recognition, scale billing operations globally, and drive automation while supporting the build-out of revenue reporting using tools like Superset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet p-rich_text_list--nested&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-list-tree=&quot;true&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Own the full revenue cycle: order-to-cash, billing, collections, revenue recognition, and month-end close.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Oversee and reconcile revenue across all our internal systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Lead the migration from manual to automated workflows; document and implement scalable processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Ensure compliance with ASC 606 across domestic and international revenue streams, including multi-element arrangements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Partner with Sales, Customer Success, and Legal to review contracts and non-standard deals for proper revenue treatment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Work with the team to oversee sales-tax, VAT/GST, and indirect tax compliance in collaboration with Anrok and external advisors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Build and maintain revenue dashboards and reporting (ARR, MRR, churn, deferred revenue waterfalls) using Superset and other BI tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Drive system integrations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Mentor a small revenue operations team and establish best-in-class practices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Support audits and serve as the primary revenue point of contact for leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Required Qualifications&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul class=&quot;p-rich_text_list p-rich_text_list__bullet p-rich_text_list--nested&quot; data-stringify-type=&quot;unordered-list&quot; data-list-tree=&quot;true&quot; data-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Bachelor’s degree in Accounting, Finance, or related field; CPA qualification&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;8+ years of progressive revenue accounting experience in SaaS, subscription, or technology companies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Deep expertise in ASC 606 and complex revenue arrangements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Strong proficiency with QuickBooks Online, Stripe Billing, Anrok (or similar tax tools), and Excel/Google Sheets; NetSuite experience a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Hands-on experience with Superset (SQL, dashboard design, data modeling).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Proven success automating manual revenue processes and scaling systems at high-growth startups.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Excellent analytical skills with meticulous attention to detail.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Strong communication skills, able to explain technical revenue topics to non-finance stakeholders.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience with international revenue (multi-currency, VAT/GST) strongly preferred.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Comfortable in a fast-paced, evolving environment&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Annual Salary Range&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;$142,000 - $200,000&lt;/p&gt;
