&lt;p class=&quot;p2&quot;&gt;Base salary is just one part of our total rewards package at xAI, which also includes equity, comprehensive medical, vision, and dental coverage, access to a 401(k) retirement plan, short &amp;amp; long-term disability insurance, life insurance, and various other discounts and perks.&lt;/p&gt;
