&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The pay for this role may range from&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;USD $35/hour - $100/hour.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your actual pay will be determined on a case-by-case basis and may vary based on the following considerations: location, job-related knowledge and skills, education, and experience.&lt;/li&gt;
