&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Install, maintain, and repair access control systems, surveillance cameras, intrusion &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;systems, and other physical security system components&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Work closely with operations, real estate, production, ˙information technology, global&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;security, and other internal teams to procure, schedule, and install devices in fast-paced, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;production critical, environments&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Collaborate with technical security team members to develop security system design&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;and installation plans&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Survey new installations, create materials lists, and maintain on-site materials inventory&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 10pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 10pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Maintain system architecture documentation based on technical security standards&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
