&lt;li&gt;Experience with other IAM platforms (e.g., Azure AD), or collaboration tools (e.g., Microsoft Teams).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with cloud environments (AWS, Azure) and containerization technologies (Docker, Kubernetes).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposure to low-code/no-code platforms, AI-enhanced automation, or workflow orchestration tools.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding of ITIL practices, or experience working in Agile operational environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in high-growth or enterprise-scale organizations with a strong security and compliance culture.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Base salary is just one part of our total rewards package at xAI, which also includes equity, comprehensive medical, vision, and dental coverage, access to a 401(k) retirement plan, short &amp;amp; long-term disability insurance, life insurance, and various other discounts and perks.&lt;/p&gt;
