&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;xAI’s mission is to create AI systems that can accurately understand the universe and aid humanity in its pursuit of knowledge. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Our team is small, highly motivated, and focused on engineering excellence. This organization is for individuals who appreciate challenging themselves and thrive on curiosity. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We operate with a flat organizational structure. All employees are expected to be hands-on and to contribute directly to the company’s mission. Leadership is given to those who show initiative and consistently deliver excellence. Work ethic and strong prioritization skills are important. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;All engineers are expected to have strong communication skills. They should be able to concisely and accurately share knowledge with their teammates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We’re seeking exceptionally talented engineers to build high-performance Mac applications that deliver seamless and intuitive user experiences. You’ll play a large role on a small team pushing the boundaries of what is possible with cutting-edge Swift-based development, with a particular focus on macOS-native features and user interfaces.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and optimize Swift-based Mac applications at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build infrastructure for large-scale data pipelines, asset management, and UI prototyping.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement quantitative evaluations for application performance, usability, and reliability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Optimization and code refinement for real-time responsiveness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop and implement strategies for handling complex, long-running tasks in macOS environments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain a deep focus on building a lovable user experience everywhere from prototyping to deployment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Additionally, experience in any of the following may set you apart&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proven track record of building SOTA Mac applications end to end alone or as part of small teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shipping high-performance desktop applications across a variety of devices and platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of releases, publications, and/or open source projects related to SwiftUI, AppKit, and macOS&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong systems and engineering skills in development frameworks like Swift, Rust, and adjacent&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technically Exceptional&lt;/strong&gt;: Engineering is your craft and you operate at the very highest level regardless of the stack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Impatient:&lt;/strong&gt; You’re excited about the mission of your work, and treat every project like you wish it had been completed yesterday.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Perfectionist:&lt;/strong&gt; You take pride in crafting the most delightful experiences for customers, and are determined to polish every last splinter from the product.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;High Agency&lt;/strong&gt;: You don’t wait for direction, and are capable of completing large projects end to end on your own.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Minded&lt;/strong&gt;: You are excited to research and build applications in order to deliver exceptional, newly enabled product experiences to customers at scale.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;We work out of xAI’s Palo Alto office and prefer that candidates are able to relocate to the Bay Area if necessary.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
