&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Swift (required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;AppKit and macOS APIs (e.g., Core Data, Core Animation) (required)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SwiftUI (required)&lt;/li&gt;
