&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Excellent problem-solving skills and ability to work in a fast-paced, dynamic environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Strong communication skills and a collaborative mindset.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bonus: Experience with Infrastructure as Code (e.g., Terraform, Ansible) or monitoring tools (e.g., Prometheus, Grafana).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
