&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Negotiate and manage high-stakes supplier contracts, including Master Service Agreements (MSAs), ensuring favorable terms, risk mitigation, and alignment with xAI’s strategic goals.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
