&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Benefits&lt;/strong&gt;: xAI offers a comprehensive benefits package, including equity, medical, vision, and dental coverage, a 401(k) retirement plan, short- and long-term disability insurance, life insurance, and various discounts and perks.&lt;/li&gt;
