&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;xAI’s mission is to create AI systems that can accurately understand the universe and aid humanity in its pursuit of knowledge. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;Our team is small, highly motivated, and focused on engineering excellence. This organization is for individuals who appreciate challenging themselves and thrive on curiosity. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;We operate with a flat organizational structure. All employees are expected to be hands-on and to contribute directly to the company’s mission. Leadership is given to those who show initiative and consistently deliver excellence. Work ethic and strong prioritization skills are important. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;All engineers are expected to have strong communication skills. They should be able to concisely and accurately share knowledge with their teammates.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Talent Engineering is a new team focused on recruiting with a first-principles and engineering mindset.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;This is a small, elite unit reporting directly to Elon.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The team works closely with both engineering and recruiting teams to create novel approaches for rapidly scaling the hiring of exceptional people.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who are you&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You believe assembling high-performance teams is an engineering problem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You love being around exceptional people and they love being around you.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are a nerdy engineer at heart, but your friends believe you are a “people person”&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ve built cool products yourself, even as a kid—perhaps personal projects, open-source contributions, or innovative hacks that demonstrate your technical creativity.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You’ve worked at organizations with incredible talent density. And you referred in great people, and helped with recruiting.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You might not be hands-on coding every day, but you’re comfortable with &quot;vibe coding&quot; and can quickly grasp technical concepts to evaluate candidates.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For any hiring need at xAI, start by asking: “Who are the absolute best people in the world for this role?” Your focus will be on developing systems to effectively identify, engage, and attract those individuals.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Once you develop the system you are also expected to execute and the hiring end to end yourself.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;We recognize that identifying the “best people” rarely happens solely on LinkedIn; instead, it occurs through referrals, networking at events, hosting competitions, leveraging specific online communities, and other creative channels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You are expected to exercise strong judgment and an intuitive understanding of what excellence looks like across various technical and non-technical domains.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interview Process&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Submit application&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;30-min intro call with a talent engineer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Presentation&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Final team onsite&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our goal is to complete the process within two weeks. All interviews will be conducted in person when applicable.&lt;/p&gt;
