&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience with CI/CD tools Github Actions and ArgoCD&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience with AWS EKS, RDS, and associated services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-stringify-indent=&quot;0&quot; data-stringify-border=&quot;0&quot;&gt;Experience with IaC tools Terraform and Puppet&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re building an extraordinary team and moving fast. If you&#39;re an exceptional engineer who shares our passion for reliability and security, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation Range&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;$180,000 - $440,000 USD&lt;/p&gt;
